====== Tag Plugin for DokuWiki (PATCHED) ======

Based on popular Tag plugin, with some patches including:
  * Add inline tag syntax (`#TAG`)

Any other modifications for core functionality in the original plugin will not be considered or discussed here.

All documentation for the Tag Plugin is available online at:

  * http://dokuwiki.org/plugin:tag

